prop.text: Hey there. Better stay away from the oasis tonight, us Tartarts are planning a raid!
Don't go rat us out, you hear!
I'm from the great C. I shouldn't wine, but this place, although sweet, is way too dry for me.
There are ruins all over the desert. Well...   in places protected from the ever moving sand dunes at least.
Every few years this oasis disappears beneath the sand dunes. Good thing the trees survive.
You look thirsty! Have some water!
Have you seen Wool Canoe? You can see it from most of the desert. It is quite a sight.

Puck: I wonder if my mother went towards Wool Canoe, the great C or maybe the bandlads.
*cough* Do you have some water? I was told there'd be an oasis, but I cant find it!
